etphoneshome.objects

Class Obstacle

  • java.lang.Object
    • etphoneshome.objects.Obstacle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Platform

    public class Obstacle
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for structures that the player and enemy cannot pass through, or can move on top of (obstacles and platforms). It acts as the parent class to the Platform class.
